quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  106,1,"Makapantag ko kiyasinanad o manga Quraish,-"
  106,2,"So kiyasinanad iran ko katho­togalin ko kapanununggao niyan a go so kakhakayao niyan,-"
  106,3,"Na Showasowata iran so Kad­nan a ungkai a Baitollah,"
  106,4,"So migai kiran sa Pangunung­kun po-on ko kaor, go miyakasarig kiran pho-on ko kaluk."
